snippet.title: New NotebookLM Upgrade Is Insane! Full Deep Research to Visuals Workflow.
snippet.description:
In this video, I walk you through a complete workflow starting with Fast Research, moving into the new Deep Research feature, and ending with fully generated visuals like infographics and mind maps.

We’ll explore how Deep Research builds a full research plan, scans hundreds of credible sources, and returns a structured, citation-rich report you can import directly into your project. Then we’ll combine those findings with a our own dataset, analyse everything side-by-side, and turn the insights into clean, ready-to-use visuals.
